data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Experience true Gainesville living with this beautiful three-bed, 1.5-bath, cozy pool home on the street where the legendary Tom Petty grew up! Thanks to this neighborhood's privacy and natural surroundings, you'll forget just how close you are to downtown. Enjoy indoor/outdoor living with large windows, a fully screened front porch, a privacy-fenced backyard, a jasmine-covered outdoor cold/hot shower, the convenience of your grill connected directly to the home's gas line, and a modern fiberglass saltwater pool with childproof fencing installed in 2017. Additionally, this home features an updated gas range, premium solid-core doors and hardware, and a jet spa bathtub.   The metal roof and hot water heater were replaced in 2014, and the new A/C in 2016.  The only thing this home is missing is YOU!
